To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MatchingLow _matchinglow;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_matchinglow = MatchingLow(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_matchinglow.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "MatchingLow Period", _matchinglow.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "MatchingLow Current", _matchinglow.Current);
}
